{"tid":2505477,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"收到選民資格確認信!!!!英國戰線唔係講笑,移民唔等於逃兵","createTime":"2021-04-26T15:25:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T09:38:33.000Z","uid":38177,"like":18,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"47ee5c7b9fbf355c604e713be4195d83bee46c13","tid":2505477,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T15:25:49.000Z","msg":"之前有登記做選民既BNO手足,應該咁上下時間會收到一封信係提你由4月28日到5月6日期間可以去你所屬選區投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到時記得帶埋封信(<span class=\"small\">信入面話唔一定要有帶,不過有埋elector number,有會方便好多</span>)<br />\n7am to 10pm可以投票,有工作人員會問你名同地址(直接比封信佢都OK)<br />\n<span class=\"red\">記住唔好比其他人睇到你投咩</span>基本上同香港一樣<br />\n<br />\n未知投邊個都唔緊要,首先，上 Who Can I Vote For 網站，填寫你的郵遞區號：<br />\n<a href=\"https://whocanivotefor.co.uk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwhocanivotefor.co.uk&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B6w7Fv2waV%2FkF2w15sEbuDLw%3D&h=5c4cc608\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://whocanivotefor.co.uk</a><br />\n網站會告訴你，你的地區有甚麼選舉。大部分地區的資訊還會顯示候選人資料，包括姓名和政黨。有些紀錄還有候選人聯絡方法！<br />\n如果找到候選人姓名但找不到聯絡方法，試着搜尋<br />\n[候選人姓名] [地區]<br />\n一般都會找到候選人或者所屬政黨地區支部的網站、社交媒體、或聯絡方法。<br />\n有時你還會找到候選人的社交媒體帳號。你可以在他們的帖文中搜尋 &ldquo;Hong Kong&rdquo;，看看他們是否已經在香港議題上表態。<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">如果都無結果,可能要靠你地去問下佢地,順便報料比其他手足一齊投票</span></span><br />\nsend email 問下佢對香港睇法.<br />\n有手足喺網上準備了幾封標準信件（<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1t49EbTJBmxr0fokTA46Nv3w44meflev0XtVndFVOf3o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1t49EbTJBmxr0fokTA46Nv3w44meflev0XtVndFVOf3o&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B6w7Fv2waV%2FkF2w15sEbuDLw%3D&h=9365af3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1t49EbTJBmxr0fokTA46Nv3w44meflev0XtVndFVOf3o</a> ），切合各級選舉，用以詢問候選人對相關香港、中國、和民主政制議題的意見。你只需剪貼相應信件內容，用電郵、臉書、或任何聯絡方法寄給你的候選人。<br />\n<br />\n最後，填寫以下表格，將候選人資料、評分、回覆內容報告給選民行動組義工：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdCY-dnE8M24KXqKsU57_Hus-MofjJN3gLjUpgXpaX9U3SItA/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdCY-dnE8M24KXqKsU57_Hus-MofjJN3gLjUpgXpaX9U3SItA%2Fviewform&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B6w7Fv2waV%2FkF2w15sEbuDLw%3D&h=ea755a0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdCY-dnE8M24KXqKsU57_Hus-MofjJN3gLjUpgXpaX9U3SItA/viewform</a> <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"gold\">依個post既資料喺D4HK嘅選民行動組度copy,</span></strong></span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">感謝D4HK嘅選民行動組同喺英國既手足付出既一切</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">香港人,加油</span>"},{"pid":"8d0347bfbc8a27a2ebc39d2eed79767ada168f8d","tid":2505477,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T15:26:49.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"ada52aa7c1c450df61ac642608797c2e947670d2","tid":2505477,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T15:38:55.000Z","msg":"英國手足蒲頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c216f7ffc02e2c8a029ef1884d99c8b15c3173c","tid":2505477,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T16:01:26.000Z","msg":"push push push<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c3fa0c37fdfff25d2657b06ba3b152b65f4cad","tid":2505477,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T16:20:45.000Z","msg":"有無英國投票功略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b8414e24d1db8fd446fdc75651dc16ae2d4ea0","tid":2505477,"uid":6946,"like":4,"dislike":15,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T16:23:10.000Z","msg":"走你就走啦 咁撚多嗲"},{"pid":"3e46488db0f59b8756d16e9fe621a23285112156","tid":2505477,"uid":38177,"like":1,"d